; Non-deleted files refer to files with 'file_is_deleted' equal to 0; 
; Full path refers to the concatenation of the directory name and the file name, separated by a slash; 
; Directory structure refers to the hierarchical organization of directories, from the root to the child directories.

Particular user refers to the user with the unique identifier (user_id) of 1; 
The time period of interest is the month of May 2023, specifically from May 1, 2023, to May 31, 2023;
Frequently accessed implies a total of more than 5 accesses.

sql:
SELECT name, size
FROM files
ORDER BY size DESC;
